{"tid":1434303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真。香港人始終要做既選擇： 港人治港 定 一國兩制","createTime":"2019-08-08T17:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T02:27:49.000Z","uid":201178,"like":62,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e614fb50552622797efed968ae01a18220f0b827","tid":1434303,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:31:15.000Z","msg":"心水清既都知，<span style=\"color: red;\">普選係中共既領導下係唔會出現，</span>如果香港人真係想有普選，就只可以有主權，又名港人治港（<span style=\"color: blue;\">港獨易入口版</span>）。<br />\n但問題就係，香港人準備好爭取自己既主權未？經濟方面又點補償？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一國兩制名存實亡，但對保守又追求民主既香港人黎講，<span style=\"color: violet;\">用呢兩個月請求中國尊重及真正實行一國兩制會係最和理非既選擇</span>。但呢一點就係<br />\n1）中國擺明會wfc一國兩制 2)只去到2047 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人係時間諗清楚自己想要咩野，我地運動方向先會更聚焦。<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港人治港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一國兩制"},{"pid":"96c0bbc63d3b4cc236ecb98a804d5376e71644cd","tid":1434303,"uid":179402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOjM9aG3xZKk&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=ab379e1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF74MRhonX28&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=a7de4042\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n有youtube喇！！！！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"af8edefdbd5d4c065c87de2f2149ac6a25b99d92","tid":1434303,"uid":201178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:34:20.000Z","msg":"諗清楚先好投"},{"pid":"6caecc21fe07af24aa7e94507c945c713c9787b0","tid":1434303,"uid":1582,"like":4,"dislike":1,"